## Industrial Standards and Specifications

This software implements or interfaces with the following industrial standards:

- **MTConnect Standard** (ANSI/MTC1.4-2018): Manufacturing Technology Connect
- **OPC Unified Architecture** (IEC 62541): Industrial communication protocol
- **ISA-95**: Enterprise-Control System Integration
- **IEC 62443**: Industrial communication networks - Network and system security

